TREMORMESH - Dual License
==========================

This project uses two licenses, mirroring open-hardware best practice:

1. HARDWARE & DOCUMENTATION  →  CERN-OHL-P v2 (Permissive)
   Applies to: schematics, board layouts, BOMs, mechanical/enclosure files,
   and design documentation under 1_*, 2_*, 3_*, and 8_Utils/.

2. SOFTWARE & FIRMWARE  →  MIT (see LICENSE-MIT)
   Applies to: all source code, including 4_Firmware/, 5_Algorithms/,
   6_Server/, 7_Simulations/, and CI scripts.

